name: AIMA-Java
tagline: Java implementation of algorithms from Norvig And Russell's "Artificial Intelligence - A Modern Approach"
body:
### Welcome to AIMA-Java.
Java implementation of algorithms from different editions of [Norvig](http://www.norvig.com/) and [Russell's](http://www.cs.berkeley.edu/~russell/)  [Artificial Intelligence - A Modern Approach](http://aima.cs.berkeley.edu/)
